					pi√π grande garanzia.
				</p>
			</div>

			<div
				class="grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-4 gap-8 text-center"
			>
				<div
					class="bg-white p-8 rounded-2xl shadow-lg border border-gray-200"
				>
					<div
						class="w-16 h-16 bg-gradient-to-br from-red-400 to-pink-500 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-4 text-white text-2xl font-bold"
					>
						‚ò∫
					</div>
					<div
						class="text-5xl font-bold text-transparent bg-clip-text bg-gradient-to-r from-red-400 to-pink-500 mb-2"
					>
						1200+
					</div>
					<p class="text-lg text-gray-600 font-medium">
						Clienti Soddisfatti
					</p>
				</div>
				<div
					class="bg-white p-8 rounded-2xl shadow-lg border border-gray-200"
				>
					<div
						class="w-16 h-16 bg-gradient-to-br from-red-400 to-pink-500 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-4 text-white text-2xl font-bold"
					>
						üèóÔ∏è
					</div>
					<div
						class="text-5xl font-bold text-transparent bg-clip-text bg-gradient-to-r from-red-400 to-pink-500 mb-2"
					>
						1500+
					</div>
					<p class="text-lg text-gray-600 font-medium">
						Progetti Completati
					</p>
				</div>
				<div
					class="bg-white p-8 rounded-2xl shadow-lg border border-gray-200"
				>
					<div
						class="w-16 h-16 bg-gradient-to-br from-red-400 to-pink-500 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-4 text-white text-2xl font-bold"
					>
						üèÖ
					</div>
					<div
						class="text-5xl font-bold text-transparent bg-clip-text bg-gradient-to-r from-red-400 to-pink-500 mb-2"
					>
						40
					</div>
					<p class="text-lg text-gray-600 font-medium">
						Anni di Esperienza
					</p>
				</div>
				<div
					class="bg-white p-8 rounded-2xl shadow-lg border border-gray-200"
				>
					<div
						class="w-16 h-16 bg-gradient-to-br from-red-400 to-pink-500 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-4 text-white text-2xl font-bold"
					>
						üë∑
					</div>
					<div
						class="text-5xl font-bold text-transparent bg-clip-text bg-gradient-to-r from-red-400 to-pink-500 mb-2"
					>
						4
					</div>
					<p class="text-lg text-gray-600 font-medium">
						Professionisti nel Team
					</p>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
	</section>

	<!-- CTA -->
	<section
		class="py-20 bg-gradient-to-br from-emerald-600 via-green-600 to-teal-600 text-white relative overflow-hidden"
	>
		<div class="absolute inset-0 opacity-10">
			<div
				class="absolute top-0 left-0 w-96 h-96 bg-white rounded-full blur-3xl"
			>
			</div>
			<div
				class="absolute bottom-0 right-0 w-96 h-96 bg-white rounded-full blur-3xl"
			>
			</div>
		</div>

		<div class="container mx-auto px-4 relative z-10">
			<div class="text-center max-w-3xl mx-auto">
				<h2 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold mb-6">
					Pronto a Iniziare il Tuo Progetto?
				</h2>
				<p class="text-xl mb-8 text-emerald-50">
					Contattaci oggi per una consulenza gratuita e scopri come
					possiamo aiutarti.
				</p>
				<a
					href="/dove-siamo"
					class="bg-white text-emerald-600 hover:bg-emerald-50 px-8 py-3 text-lg rounded-full shadow-xl hover:shadow-2xl transition-all inline-flex items-center gap-2"
				>
					Contattaci Ora ‚Üí
				</a>
			</div>
		</div>
	</section>
</BaseLayout>
